OL,3,CLocal council to 'work with' schools
OL,4,Cto comply with single-sex toilets
OL,5,Cguidance
OL,7,FDumfries and Galloway Council has
OL,8,Fconfirmed it will work with local
OL,9,Fschools to make sure separate toilets
OL,10,Fare available for boys and girls.
OL,12,FNew guidance from the Scottish
OL,13,FGovernment says facilities must be
OL,14,Fmade available based on biological sex.
OL,16,FSchools can also provide gender
OL,17,Fneutral toilets, alongside the single-
OL,18,Fsex facilities.
