OL,3,CLocal council to 'work with' schools
OL,4,Cto comply with single-sex toilets
OL,5,Cguidance
OL,7,FPreviously, schools had been told that
OL,8,Ftransgender pupils could use whichever
OL,9,Ffacilities they felt comfortable in.
OL,11,FThe updated guidance from ministers in
OL,12,FHolyrood follows the Supreme Court's
OL,13,Fruling in April 2025, that a woman is
OL,14,Fdefined by biological sex.
OL,16,FAnother ruling later in April stated
OL,17,Fthat schools in Scotland must provide
OL,18,Fsingle-sex toilets.
