OL,3,CLocal council to 'work with' schools
OL,4,Cto comply with single-sex toilets
OL,5,Cguidance
OL,7,FThe Scottish Government's updated
OL,8,Fguidance was published on Monday 29
OL,9,FSeptember, and says that facilities
OL,10,Fmust be available "on the basis of
OL,11,Fbiological sex", and that local
OL,12,Fauthorities should "consider" also
OL,13,Fincluding gender neutral provision for
OL,14,Ftransgender pupils.
OL,16,FIn a statement, Dumfries and Galloway
OL,17,FCouncil told ITV Border it
OL,18,F"acknowledges" the guidance, and will
OL,19,F"work with school management teams" to
OL,20,Fmake any necessary changes.
