OL,3,CLocal council to 'work with' schools
OL,4,Cto comply with single-sex toilets
OL,5,Cguidance
OL,7,FIt says older schools in the region
OL,8,Falready have separate toilets for boys
OL,9,Fand girls, but some newer or
OL,10,Frefurbished facilities have "open plan
OL,11,Fwash areas".
OL,13,FThese areas, the council says, are
OL,14,F"flexible and can be gender neutral or
OL,15,Fgender specific as required", and
OL,16,Fofficials will work with school staff
OL,17,Fto ensure they comply with the new
OL,18,Fguidance.
